utton">Apply Now</a><a href="/schedule-a-tour" class="master-button w-button">Schedule A Tour</a></div></div></section><section class="primary-section no-overflow"><div class="w-layout-blockcontainer primary-container w-container"><h2 class="location-header">OUR FLEET</h2><div class="page-body-text centered">Our <strong>Piper Archer TX (P100i) fleet</strong> is the backbone of our flight training program, offering students a modern, reliable, and safe aircraft to build their skills. Equipped with <strong>Garmin G1000 NXi avionics</strong>, these aircraft provide advanced navigation and situational awareness, mirroring the technology found in commercial and corporate aviation. The <strong>Piper 100i’s fuel efficiency, stable flight characteristics, and durable design</strong> make it an ideal platform for both beginner and advanced flight training. With a focus on <strong>safety, comfort, and cutting-edge technology</strong>, our Piper fleet ensures that students are well-prepared for their aviation careers.</div><div class="fleet-tool-tip-holder"><img src="images/piper-mockup.png" loading="lazy" sizes="(max-width: 479px) 100vw, (max-width: 991px) 700px, 96vw" srcset="images/piper-mockup-p-500.png 500w, images/piper-mockup-p-800.png 800w, images/piper-mockup.png 1024w" alt="" class="image-15"/><div class="div-block-3"><a href="#" class="tooltip safety w-inline-block"><div class="tooltip-contain tires"><img src="images/21_20_pilot-100i_panel_24-1024x474.jpg" loading="lazy" sizes="100vw" srcset="images/21_20_pilot-100i_panel_24-1024x474-p-500.jpg 500w, images/21_20_pilot-100i_panel_24-1024x474-p-800.jpg 800w, images/21_20_pilot-100i_panel_24-1024x474.jpg 1024w" alt="" class="tool-tip-image"/><div class="text-for-tooltip">Situational awareness on the ground is as important as it is in the air, and with Garmin SafeTaxi, you can display airport diagrams (for over 1,300 airports in the United States, with additional coverage in Europe and Canada) with your aircraft position georeferenced right on the Pilot 100i’s MFD.</div></div></a><a href="#" class="tooltip avionics w-inline-block"><div class="tooltip-contain front"><img src="images/21_20_pilot-100i_panel_24-1024x474.jpg" loading="lazy" sizes="100vw" srcset="images/21_20_pilot-100i_panel_24-1024x474-p-500.jpg 500w, images/21_20_pilot-100i_panel_24-1024x474-p-800.jpg 800w, images/21_20_pilot-100i_panel_24-1024x474.jpg 1024w" alt="" class="tool-tip-image"/><div class="text-for-tooltip">Our entire fleet features <strong>Garmin G3X Touch (10.6” PFD/MFD)</strong> with Connext® technology, supported by a <strong>Garmin G5 standby display</strong>. It features a <strong>GFC500 autopilot with Electronic Stability Protection</strong> and a <strong>GNX 375 touchscreen navigator with ADS-B In &amp; Out</strong>. Communication and navigation are handled by a <strong>GNC 255A NAV/Comm radio</strong>, a <strong>GTR 20 second VHF COM radio</strong>, and a <strong>GMA 245R remote audio panel with Bluetooth</strong>. Additional features include <strong>moving map, terrain and traffic alerts, synthetic vision, flight data logging, and a wet compass</strong>.</div></div></a><a href="#" class="tooltip tech w-inline-block"><div class="tooltip-contain middle"><img src="images/20_pilot-100i_interiors_07-1650x1100-20-1-.jpg" loading="lazy" sizes="100vw" srcset="images/20_pilot-100i_interiors_07-1650x1100-20-1-p-500.jpg 500w, images/20_pilot-100i_interiors_07-1650x1100-20-1-p-800.jpg 800w, images/20_pilot-100i_interiors_07-1650x1100-20-1-p-1080.jpg 1080w, images/20_pilot-100i_interiors_07-1650x1100-20-1-p-1600.jpg 1600w, images/20_pilot-100i_interiors_07-1650x1100-20-1-.jpg 1650w" alt="" class="tool-tip-image"/><div class="text-for-tooltip">The Pilot 100i interior is ready for high flight hours while still providing maximum comfort and durability. Highly durable interior features and cabin appointments create the ultimate training environment, with ergonomically designed power plugs, lighting controls and switching. You can even add a third seat for an observer.</div></div></a><a href="#" class="tooltip stable w-inline-block"><div class="tooltip-contain rear"><img src="images/w221129_252.jpg" loading="lazy" sizes="100vw" srcset="images/w221129_252-p-500.jpg 500w, images/w221129_252-p-800.jpg 800w, images/w221129_252-p-1080.jpg 1080w, images/w221129_252-p-1600.jpg 1600w, images/w221129_252.jpg 1800w" alt="" class="tool-tip-image"/><div class="text-for-tooltip">Piper’s engineering and design teams put generations of expertise and leadership into the design of the Pilot 100i – optimized for flight training efficiency, effectiveness and safety. Students, instructors and training managers will appreciate the durable interior, designed for high flight time training operations.</div></div></a></div></div></div></section><section class="primary-section"><div class="location-header">HEAR FROM OUR STUDENTS</div><div data-delay="4000" data-animation="slide" class="slider w-slider" data-autoplay="false" data-easing="ease" data-hide-arrows="false" data-disable-swipe="false" data-autoplay-limit="0" data-nav-spacing="3" data-duration="500" data-infinite="true"><div class="mask w-slider-mask"><div class="video---reels w-slide"><div style="padding-top:75%" class="video w-video w-embed"><iframe class="embedly-embed" src="//cdn.embedly.com/widgets/media.html?src=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FgalV-RBuPBY%3Ffeature%3Doembed%26modestbranding%3D0%26showinfo%3D0%26controls%3D0&display_name=YouTube&url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fshorts%2FgalV-RBuPBY%3Fshowinfo%3D0%26modestbranding%3D0%26controls%3D0&image=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FgalV-RBuPBY%2Fhq2.jpg&type=text%2Fhtml&schema=youtube" width="940" height="705" scrolling="no" allowfullscreen title="Career Shift - Lee Balduzzi"></iframe></div></div><div class="video---reels w-slide"><div style="padding-top:75%" class="video w-video w-embed"><iframe class="embedly-embed" src="//cdn.embedly.com/widgets/media.html?src=https%3